{"tid":1422642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[再開過]學生妹都拉？！天水圍死黑警我屌你老母","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:41:14.000Z","uid":161551,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"864624d2f6f9c0f3c116388697ce462183044371","tid":1422642,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好意思呃左大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n借朋友Acc出post 信唔信由你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前言：<br />\n警方拘捕一名13歲小童<br />\n涉嫌非法集結、襲警、藏有攻擊性武器等<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1421970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1421970</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係天水圍發夢既咁多位可能未知尋日發生咩事<br />\n我簡單講下先啦：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有個中二女學生去完學校拎書返屋企就俾狗拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我啊妹個同學就係當事人，佢琴日12點左右去完鄧XX中學攞書之後就準備返屋企。當佢行到天盛商場個時咁啱班狗開始咬人。而個同學走唔切就俾狗拉左，入左狗屋。<br />\n同學既啊媽同埋校長去到狗屋之後班狗都唔肯放人。<br />\n宜家就告嗰個女仔4條罪：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非法集結、襲警、藏有攻擊性武器</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我想講既係：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你班仆街冚家剷連學生妹都拉，仲有無良心㗎？！人地去攞書就藏有攻擊性武器？攞書掉你咩？<ins><strong>定係F.3既課程難到你班毅進仔搞到你頭痛啊？</strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />非法集結我都唔理啦，但係一個13歲學生妹點襲警啊仆你個街！個胸又未發育又無力點襲啊？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你班黑警都係想嚇我地啲學生，搞到我地唔敢出黎姐。<br />\n不過...... <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我點樣都會出黎㗎啦 你打我啊笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n追究黑警知法犯法</span></span><br />\n<br />\np.s.頭先個Post我都知衰㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知錯㗎啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wM3NvZE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwM3NvZE.gif&h=d3b0f963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cXbddm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cXbddm.png&h=906e8c21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e38f1c34fb9ae4910703bc2894dfc2d4ea620f6f","tid":1422642,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n我知錯啦"},{"pid":"2ddfd77992dd899073581658de61d8201ba2ec4c","tid":1422642,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:32:10.000Z","msg":"自推2<br />\n我知錯啦"},{"pid":"5a577a097bbdf162f16bdf0b0639cd44991e078b","tid":1422642,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"自推2<br />\n我知錯啦"},{"pid":"4177e3765fc9140bc35c2d827365f76ccb0a98e4","tid":1422642,"uid":135475,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odO2jT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodO2jT6.jpg&h=d9953baa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6saTryV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6saTryV.jpg&h=47f1ff3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1684ce163bde271fff3b20b478a99a074ee2df4f","tid":1422642,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n我知錯啦<br />\n來生不做標題黨<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同埋支那人</span>"},{"pid":"71f51b6422f07881222ee519ec06c4e